name: Liberation of the true self
description:
This is a shader art piece that represents the struggle of the individual to find the true nature of himself. 

This is a colaboration with KALI (one of the shader gods) , we made it together in a shader jam. I have his permission to publish it and half of the earnings of this sell are going to him 

You can check the original shader at shadertoy : https://www.shadertoy.com/view/tlGfzdA
